divs: Sighting DetailsStanding outside the carport of our home and taking pictures of sudden fierce storm clouds during an unusual power outage. When we uploaded the pics and enlarged them we saw the 5 objects shown in the pictures (picture 5). Picture 6 has one object still in the frame and picture 4 shows the funnel effect originally. We did not know there were going to be objects in photographs when they were originally taken.
Summary: 5 objects in storm clouds not seen until enlarged digital photo was viewed
